Figure~\ref{fig:timeouts_mobility} demonstrates \alg{} w/ MP effectiveness against mobility-induced failures, validating its ability to anticipate handover events through velocity vector analysis. Specifically, \alg{} w/ MP reduces mobility-induced failures by 85.09\% compared to FedAvg, demonstrating superior adaptability to vehicular movement.
